      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is nothing short of meticulous. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defies its pre-owned status, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
