      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it is in such stunning, pristine condition that you\u2019ll feel like you\u2019re driving it right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it runs like an absolute dream. It\u2019s rare to find one that\u2019s been this well-loved and looked after. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
